      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="wxpy环境搭建"><a href="#wxpy环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="wxpy环境搭建"></a>wxpy环境搭建</h1><h2 id="What-is-wxpy"><a href="#What-is-wxpy" class="headerlink" title="What is wxpy?"></a>What is wxpy?</h2><p>wxpy 在 itchat 的基础上，通过大量接口优化提升了模块的易用性，并进行丰富的功能扩展。</p><h2 id="How-to-install-wxpy"><a href="#How-to-install-wxpy" class="headerlink" title="How to install wxpy?"></a>How to install wxpy?</h2><p>Mac or Ubuntu:<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pip3 install wxpy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>Windows:<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install wxpy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="初识wxpy"><a href="#初识wxpy" class="headerlink" title="初识wxpy"></a>初识wxpy</h1><h2 id="登录微信"><a href="#登录微信" class="headerlink" title="登录微信"></a>登录微信</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> wxpy </span><br><span class="line">bot = wxpy.Bot()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>扫描二维码，即可登陆你的微信。</p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-e0e096e1da6f1a46.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/700" alt=""></p><h2 id="获取好友"><a href="#获取好友" class="headerlink" title="获取好友"></a>获取好友</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">my_friends = bot.friends()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> friend <span class="keyword">in</span> my_friends():</span><br><span class="line">print(friend)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-6934721854cfc00d.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/490" alt=""></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-cd6705fb1c6cdb57.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/480" alt=""></p><h2 id="统计好友性别"><a href="#统计好友性别" class="headerlink" title="统计好友性别"></a>统计好友性别</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sex_dict = &#123;<span class="string">'male'</span>: <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="string">'female'</span>: <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="string">'other'</span>: <span class="number">0</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> friend <span class="keyword">in</span> my_friends:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> friend.sex == <span class="number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        sex_dict[<span class="string">'male'</span>] += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">elif</span> friend.sex == <span class="number">2</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        sex_dict[<span class="string">'female'</span>] += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        sex_dict[<span class="string">'other'</span>] += <spa